{
  "video_id": "iP9QF_lBOyA",
  "title": "Ray Anderson: The business logic of sustainability",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 18330.0,
      "end_time": 22330.0,
      "text": "Believe me or not, I come offering a solution"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 22330.0,
      "end_time": 26330.0,
      "text": "to a very important part of this larger problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 26330.0,
      "end_time": 28330.0,
      "text": "with the requisite focus on climate."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 28330.0,
      "end_time": 30330.0,
      "text": "And the solution I offer"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 30330.0,
      "end_time": 32330.0,
      "text": "is to the biggest culprit"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 32330.0,
      "end_time": 36330.0,
      "text": "in this massive mistreatment of the earth"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 36330.0,
      "end_time": 38330.0,
      "text": "by humankind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 38330.0,
      "end_time": 41330.0,
      "text": "and the resulting decline of the biosphere."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 41330.0,
      "end_time": 44330.0,
      "text": "That culprit is business and industry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 44330.0,
      "end_time": 47330.0,
      "text": "which happens to be where I have spent the last 52 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 47330.0,
      "end_time": 51330.0,
      "text": "since my graduation from Georgia Tech in 1956."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 51330.0,
      "end_time": 53330.0,
      "text": "As an industrial engineer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 53330.0,
      "end_time": 57330.0,
      "text": "cum aspiring and then successful entrepreneur."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 57330.0,
      "end_time": 60330.0,
      "text": "After founding my company, Interface, from scratch"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 60330.0,
      "end_time": 63330.0,
      "text": "in 1973, 36 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 63330.0,
      "end_time": 65330.0,
      "text": "to produce carpet tiles in America"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 65330.0,
      "end_time": 68330.0,
      "text": "for the business and institution markets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 68330.0,
      "end_time": 71330.0,
      "text": "and shepherding it through start-up and survival"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 71330.0,
      "end_time": 74330.0,
      "text": "to prosperity and global dominance in its field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 74330.0,
      "end_time": 76330.0,
      "text": "I read Paul Hawken&#39;s book,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 76330.0,
      "end_time": 78330.0,
      "text": "\"The Ecology of Commerce,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 78330.0,
      "end_time": 81330.0,
      "text": "the summer of 1994."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 81330.0,
      "end_time": 84330.0,
      "text": "In his book, Paul charges business and industry"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 84330.0,
      "end_time": 87330.0,
      "text": "as, one, the major culprit"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 87330.0,
      "end_time": 89330.0,
      "text": "in causing the decline of the biosphere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 89330.0,
      "end_time": 92330.0,
      "text": "and, two, the only institution that is large enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 92330.0,
      "end_time": 94330.0,
      "text": "and pervasive enough, and powerful enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 94330.0,
      "end_time": 98330.0,
      "text": "to really lead humankind out of this mess."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 98330.0,
      "end_time": 101330.0,
      "text": "And by the way he convicted me"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 101330.0,
      "end_time": 103330.0,
      "text": "as a plunderer of the earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 103330.0,
      "end_time": 106330.0,
      "text": "And I then challenged the people of Interface, my company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 106330.0,
      "end_time": 110330.0,
      "text": "to lead our company and the entire industrial world to sustainability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 110330.0,
      "end_time": 112330.0,
      "text": "which we defined as eventually operating"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 112330.0,
      "end_time": 115330.0,
      "text": "our petroleum-intensive company in such a way"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 115330.0,
      "end_time": 117330.0,
      "text": "as to take from the earth"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 117330.0,
      "end_time": 121330.0,
      "text": "only what can be renewed by the earth, naturally and rapidly --"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 121330.0,
      "end_time": 123330.0,
      "text": "not another fresh drop of oil --"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 123330.0,
      "end_time": 127330.0,
      "text": "and to do no harm to the biosphere."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 127330.0,
      "end_time": 129329.0,
      "text": "Take nothing: do no harm."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 129330.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131330.0,
      "text": "I simply said, \"If Hawken is right"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 131330.0,
      "end_time": 133330.0,
      "text": "and business and industry must lead,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 133330.0,
      "end_time": 135330.0,
      "text": "who will lead business and industry?"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 135330.0,
      "end_time": 138330.0,
      "text": "Unless somebody leads, nobody will.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 138330.0,
      "end_time": 141330.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s axiomatic. Why not us?"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 141330.0,
      "end_time": 143330.0,
      "text": "And thanks to the people of Interface,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 143330.0,
      "end_time": 146330.0,
      "text": "I have become a recovering plunderer."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 146330.0,
      "end_time": 147330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 147330.0,
      "end_time": 152330.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 152330.0,
      "end_time": 156330.0,
      "text": "I once told a Fortune Magazine writer"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 156330.0,
      "end_time": 159330.0,
      "text": "that someday people like me would go to jail."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 159330.0,
      "end_time": 161330.0,
      "text": "And that became the headline of a Fortune article."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 161330.0,
      "end_time": 165330.0,
      "text": "They went on to describe me as America&#39;s greenest CEO."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 165330.0,
      "end_time": 168330.0,
      "text": "From plunderer to recovering plunderer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 168330.0,
      "end_time": 171330.0,
      "text": "to America&#39;s greenest CEO in five years --"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 171330.0,
      "end_time": 173330.0,
      "text": "that, frankly, was a pretty sad commentary"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 173330.0,
      "end_time": 178330.0,
      "text": "on American CEOs in 1999."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 178330.0,
      "end_time": 181330.0,
      "text": "Asked later in the Canadian documentary, \"The Corporation,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 181330.0,
      "end_time": 184330.0,
      "text": "what I meant by the \"go to jail\" remark,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 184330.0,
      "end_time": 188330.0,
      "text": "I offered that theft is a crime."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 188330.0,
      "end_time": 193330.0,
      "text": "And theft of our children&#39;s future would someday be a crime."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 193330.0,
      "end_time": 195330.0,
      "text": "But I realized, for that to be true --"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 195330.0,
      "end_time": 198330.0,
      "text": "for theft of our children&#39;s future to be a crime --"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 198330.0,
      "end_time": 201330.0,
      "text": "there must be a clear, demonstrable alternative"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 201330.0,
      "end_time": 204330.0,
      "text": "to the take-make-waste industrial system"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 204330.0,
      "end_time": 207330.0,
      "text": "that so dominates our civilization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 207330.0,
      "end_time": 210330.0,
      "text": "and is the major culprit, stealing our children&#39;s future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 210330.0,
      "end_time": 212330.0,
      "text": "by digging up the earth"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 212330.0,
      "end_time": 216330.0,
      "text": "and converting it to products that quickly become waste"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 216330.0,
      "end_time": 218330.0,
      "text": "in a landfill or an incinerator --"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 218330.0,
      "end_time": 223330.0,
      "text": "in short, digging up the earth and converting it to pollution."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 223330.0,
      "end_time": 225330.0,
      "text": "According to Paul and Anne Ehrlich"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 225330.0,
      "end_time": 228330.0,
      "text": "and a well-known environmental impact equation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 228330.0,
      "end_time": 230330.0,
      "text": "impact -- a bad thing --"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 230330.0,
      "end_time": 234330.0,
      "text": "is the product of population, affluence and technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 234330.0,
      "end_time": 238330.0,
      "text": "That is, impact is generated by people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 238330.0,
      "end_time": 240330.0,
      "text": "what they consume in their affluence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 240330.0,
      "end_time": 243330.0,
      "text": "and how it is produced."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 243330.0,
      "end_time": 245330.0,
      "text": "And though the equation is largely subjective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 245330.0,
      "end_time": 249330.0,
      "text": "you can perhaps quantify people, and perhaps quantify affluence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 249330.0,
      "end_time": 253330.0,
      "text": "but technology is abusive in too many ways to quantify."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 253330.0,
      "end_time": 255330.0,
      "text": "So the equation is conceptual."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 255330.0,
      "end_time": 258330.0,
      "text": "Still it works to help us understand the problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 258329.0,
      "end_time": 263330.0,
      "text": "So we set out at Interface, in 1994,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 263330.0,
      "end_time": 265330.0,
      "text": "to create an example:"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 265330.0,
      "end_time": 267330.0,
      "text": "to transform the way we made carpet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 267330.0,
      "end_time": 271330.0,
      "text": "a petroleum-intensive product for materials as well as energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 271330.0,
      "end_time": 273330.0,
      "text": "and to transform our technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 273330.0,
      "end_time": 276330.0,
      "text": "so they diminished environmental impact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 276330.0,
      "end_time": 279330.0,
      "text": "rather than multiplied it."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 279330.0,
      "end_time": 282330.0,
      "text": "Paul and Anne Ehrlich&#39;s environmental impact equation:"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 282330.0,
      "end_time": 285330.0,
      "text": "I is equal to P times A times T:"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 285330.0,
      "end_time": 288330.0,
      "text": "population, affluence and technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 288330.0,
      "end_time": 294330.0,
      "text": "I wanted Interface to rewrite that equation so that it read"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 294330.0,
      "end_time": 297330.0,
      "text": "I equals P times A divided by T."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 297330.0,
      "end_time": 300330.0,
      "text": "Now, the mathematically-minded will see immediately"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 300330.0,
      "end_time": 303330.0,
      "text": "that T in the numerator increases impact -- a bad thing --"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 303330.0,
      "end_time": 307330.0,
      "text": "but T in the denominator decreases impact."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 307330.0,
      "end_time": 311330.0,
      "text": "So I ask, \"What would move T, technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 311330.0,
      "end_time": 313330.0,
      "text": "from the numerator -- call it T1 --"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 313330.0,
      "end_time": 315330.0,
      "text": "where it increases impact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 315330.0,
      "end_time": 318330.0,
      "text": "to the denominator -- call it T2 --"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 318330.0,
      "end_time": 321330.0,
      "text": "where it reduces impact?"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 321330.0,
      "end_time": 325330.0,
      "text": "I thought about the characteristics"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 325330.0,
      "end_time": 327330.0,
      "text": "of first industrial revolution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 327330.0,
      "end_time": 330330.0,
      "text": "T1, as we practiced it at Interface,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 330330.0,
      "end_time": 334330.0,
      "text": "and it had the following characteristics."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 334330.0,
      "end_time": 338330.0,
      "text": "Extractive: taking raw materials from the earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 338330.0,
      "end_time": 341330.0,
      "text": "Linear: take, make, waste."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 341330.0,
      "end_time": 343330.0,
      "text": "Powered by fossil fuel-derived energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 343330.0,
      "end_time": 347330.0,
      "text": "Wasteful: abusive and focused on labor productivity."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 347330.0,
      "end_time": 350330.0,
      "text": "More carpet per man-hour."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 350330.0,
      "end_time": 353330.0,
      "text": "Thinking it through, I realized that all those attributes"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 353330.0,
      "end_time": 358330.0,
      "text": "must be changed to move T to the denominator."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 358330.0,
      "end_time": 363330.0,
      "text": "In the new industrial revolution extractive must be replaced by renewable;"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 363330.0,
      "end_time": 365330.0,
      "text": "linear by cyclical;"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 365330.0,
      "end_time": 369330.0,
      "text": "fossil fuel energy by renewable energy, sunlight;"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 369330.0,
      "end_time": 371330.0,
      "text": "wasteful by waste-free;"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 371330.0,
      "end_time": 373330.0,
      "text": "and abusive by benign;"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 373330.0,
      "end_time": 377330.0,
      "text": "and labor productivity by resource productivity."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 377330.0,
      "end_time": 381330.0,
      "text": "And I reasoned that if we could make those transformative changes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 381330.0,
      "end_time": 383330.0,
      "text": "and get rid of T1 altogether,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 383330.0,
      "end_time": 386330.0,
      "text": "we could reduce our impact to zero,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 386330.0,
      "end_time": 389330.0,
      "text": "including our impact on the climate."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 389330.0,
      "end_time": 392330.0,
      "text": "And that became the Interface plan in 1995,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 392330.0,
      "end_time": 395330.0,
      "text": "and has been the plan ever since."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 395330.0,
      "end_time": 399330.0,
      "text": "We have measured our progress very rigorously."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 399330.0,
      "end_time": 403330.0,
      "text": "So I can tell you how far we have come in the ensuing 12 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 403330.0,
      "end_time": 405330.0,
      "text": "Net greenhouse gas emissions"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 405330.0,
      "end_time": 409330.0,
      "text": "down 82 percent in absolute tonnage."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 409330.0,
      "end_time": 413330.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 413330.0,
      "end_time": 415330.0,
      "text": "Over the same span of time"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 415330.0,
      "end_time": 418330.0,
      "text": "sales have increased by two-thirds and profits have doubled."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 418330.0,
      "end_time": 421330.0,
      "text": "So an 82 percent absolute reduction"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 421330.0,
      "end_time": 423330.0,
      "text": "translates into a 90 percent reduction"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 423330.0,
      "end_time": 427330.0,
      "text": "in greenhouse gas intensity relative to sales."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 427330.0,
      "end_time": 429330.0,
      "text": "This is the magnitude"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 429330.0,
      "end_time": 432330.0,
      "text": "of the reduction the entire global technosphere"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 432330.0,
      "end_time": 435330.0,
      "text": "must realize by 2050"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 435330.0,
      "end_time": 438330.0,
      "text": "to avoid catastrophic climate disruption --"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 438330.0,
      "end_time": 441330.0,
      "text": "so the scientists are telling us."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 441330.0,
      "end_time": 445330.0,
      "text": "Fossil fuel usage is down 60 percent per unit of production,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 445330.0,
      "end_time": 447330.0,
      "text": "due to efficiencies in renewables."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 447330.0,
      "end_time": 450330.0,
      "text": "The cheapest, most secure barrel of oil there is"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 450330.0,
      "end_time": 453330.0,
      "text": "is the one not used through efficiencies."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 453330.0,
      "end_time": 456330.0,
      "text": "Water usage is down 75 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 456330.0,
      "end_time": 458330.0,
      "text": "in our worldwide carpet tile business."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 458330.0,
      "end_time": 461330.0,
      "text": "Down 40 percent in our broadloom carpet business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 461330.0,
      "end_time": 463330.0,
      "text": "which we acquired in 1993"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 463330.0,
      "end_time": 465330.0,
      "text": "right here in California, City of Industry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 465330.0,
      "end_time": 468330.0,
      "text": "where water is so precious."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 468330.0,
      "end_time": 472330.0,
      "text": "Renewable or recyclable materials are 25 percent of the total, and growing rapidly."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 472330.0,
      "end_time": 475330.0,
      "text": "Renewable energy is 27 percent of our total,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 475330.0,
      "end_time": 477330.0,
      "text": "going for 100 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 477330.0,
      "end_time": 480330.0,
      "text": "We have diverted 148 million pounds --"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 480330.0,
      "end_time": 482330.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s 74,000 tons --"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 482330.0,
      "end_time": 485330.0,
      "text": "of used carpet from landfills,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 485330.0,
      "end_time": 487330.0,
      "text": "closing the loop on material flows"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 487330.0,
      "end_time": 489330.0,
      "text": "through reverse logistics"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 489330.0,
      "end_time": 492330.0,
      "text": "and post-consumer recycling technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 492330.0,
      "end_time": 496330.0,
      "text": "that did not exist when we started 14 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 496330.0,
      "end_time": 498330.0,
      "text": "Those new cyclical technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 498330.0,
      "end_time": 501330.0,
      "text": "have contributed mightily to the fact that we have produced and sold"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 501330.0,
      "end_time": 505330.0,
      "text": "85 million square yards of climate-neutral carpet"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 505330.0,
      "end_time": 507330.0,
      "text": "since 2004,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 507330.0,
      "end_time": 511330.0,
      "text": "meaning no net contribution to global climate disruption"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 511330.0,
      "end_time": 513329.0,
      "text": "in producing the carpet throughout the supply chain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 513330.00000000006,
      "end_time": 518330.00000000006,
      "text": "from mine and well head clear to end-of-life reclamation --"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 518330.00000000006,
      "end_time": 520330.00000000006,
      "text": "independent third-party certified."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 520330.00000000006,
      "end_time": 523330.00000000006,
      "text": "We call it Cool Carpet."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 523330.00000000006,
      "end_time": 526330.0,
      "text": "And it has been a powerful marketplace differentiator,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 526330.0,
      "end_time": 528330.0,
      "text": "increasing sales and profits."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 528330.0,
      "end_time": 532330.0,
      "text": "Three years ago we launched carpet tile for the home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 532330.0,
      "end_time": 534330.0,
      "text": "under the brand Flor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 534330.0,
      "end_time": 537330.0,
      "text": "misspelled F-L-O-R."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 537330.0,
      "end_time": 539330.0,
      "text": "You can point and click today at Flor.com"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 539330.0,
      "end_time": 543330.0,
      "text": "and have Cool Carpet delivered to your front door in five days."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 543330.0,
      "end_time": 546330.0,
      "text": "It is practical, and pretty too."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 546330.0,
      "end_time": 547330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 547330.0,
      "end_time": 553330.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 553330.0,
      "end_time": 555330.0,
      "text": "We reckon that we are a bit over halfway"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 555330.0,
      "end_time": 560330.0,
      "text": "to our goal: zero impact, zero footprint."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 560330.0,
      "end_time": 563330.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve set 2020 as our target year for zero,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 563330.0,
      "end_time": 568330.0,
      "text": "for reaching the top, the summit of Mount Sustainability."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 568330.0,
      "end_time": 570330.0,
      "text": "We call this Mission Zero."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 570330.0,
      "end_time": 573330.0,
      "text": "And this is perhaps the most important facet:"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 573330.0,
      "end_time": 577330.0,
      "text": "we have found Mission Zero to be incredibly good for business."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 577330.0,
      "end_time": 580330.0,
      "text": "A better business model,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 580330.0,
      "end_time": 582330.0,
      "text": "a better way to bigger profits."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 582330.0,
      "end_time": 585330.0,
      "text": "Here is the business case for sustainability."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 585330.0,
      "end_time": 589330.0,
      "text": "From real life experience, costs are down, not up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 589330.0,
      "end_time": 591330.0,
      "text": "reflecting some 400 million dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 591330.0,
      "end_time": 595330.0,
      "text": "of avoided costs in pursuit of zero waste --"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 595330.0,
      "end_time": 598330.0,
      "text": "the first face of Mount Sustainability."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 598330.0,
      "end_time": 602330.0,
      "text": "This has paid all the costs for the transformation of Interface."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 602330.0,
      "end_time": 604330.0,
      "text": "And this dispels a myth too,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 604330.0,
      "end_time": 608330.0,
      "text": "this false choice between the environment and the economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 608330.0,
      "end_time": 610330.0,
      "text": "Our products are the best they&#39;ve ever been,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 610330.0,
      "end_time": 612330.0,
      "text": "inspired by design for sustainability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 612330.0,
      "end_time": 616330.0,
      "text": "an unexpected wellspring of innovation."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 616330.0,
      "end_time": 619330.0,
      "text": "Our people are galvanized around this shared higher purpose."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 619330.0,
      "end_time": 621330.0,
      "text": "You cannot beat it for attracting the best people"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 621330.0,
      "end_time": 624330.0,
      "text": "and bringing them together."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 624330.0,
      "end_time": 627330.0,
      "text": "And the goodwill of the marketplace is astonishing."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 627330.0,
      "end_time": 631330.0,
      "text": "No amount of advertising, no clever marketing campaign,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 631330.0,
      "end_time": 634330.0,
      "text": "at any price, could have produced or created"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 634330.0,
      "end_time": 637330.0,
      "text": "this much goodwill."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 637330.0,
      "end_time": 639330.0,
      "text": "Costs, products, people, marketplaces --"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 639330.0,
      "end_time": 641330.0,
      "text": "what else is there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 641330.0,
      "end_time": 643330.0,
      "text": "It is a better business model."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 643330.0,
      "end_time": 648330.0,
      "text": "And here is our 14-year record of sales and profits."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 648330.0,
      "end_time": 651330.0,
      "text": "There is a dip there, from 2001 to 2003:"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 651330.0,
      "end_time": 653330.0,
      "text": "a dip when our sales, over a three-year period,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 653330.0,
      "end_time": 655330.0,
      "text": "were down 17 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 655330.0,
      "end_time": 658330.0,
      "text": "But the marketplace was down 36 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 658330.0,
      "end_time": 660330.0,
      "text": "We literally gained market share."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 660330.0,
      "end_time": 663330.0,
      "text": "We might not have survived that recession"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 663330.0,
      "end_time": 666330.0,
      "text": "but for the advantages of sustainability."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 666330.0,
      "end_time": 670330.0,
      "text": "If every business were pursuing Interface plans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 670330.0,
      "end_time": 672330.0,
      "text": "would that solve all our problems?"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 672330.0,
      "end_time": 674330.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t think so."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 674330.0,
      "end_time": 677330.0,
      "text": "I remain troubled by the revised Ehrlich equation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 677330.0,
      "end_time": 681330.0,
      "text": "I equals P times A divided by T2."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 681330.0,
      "end_time": 683330.0,
      "text": "That A is a capital A,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 683330.0,
      "end_time": 688330.0,
      "text": "suggesting that affluence is an end in itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 688330.0,
      "end_time": 692330.0,
      "text": "But what if we reframed Ehrlich further?"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 692330.0,
      "end_time": 695330.0,
      "text": "And what if we made A a lowercase &#39;a,&#39;"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 695330.0,
      "end_time": 697330.0,
      "text": "suggesting that it is a means to an end,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 697330.0,
      "end_time": 700330.0,
      "text": "and that end is happiness --"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 700330.0,
      "end_time": 703330.0,
      "text": "more happiness with less stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 703330.0,
      "end_time": 706330.0,
      "text": "You know that would reframe civilization itself --"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 706330.0,
      "end_time": 714330.0,
      "text": "(Applause) --"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 714330.0,
      "end_time": 717330.0,
      "text": "and our whole system of economics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 717330.0,
      "end_time": 723330.0,
      "text": "if not for our species, then perhaps for the one that succeeds us:"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 723330.0,
      "end_time": 726330.0,
      "text": "the sustainable species, living on a finite earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 726330.0,
      "end_time": 729330.0,
      "text": "ethically, happily and ecologically"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 729330.0,
      "end_time": 731330.0,
      "text": "in balance with nature"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 731330.0,
      "end_time": 734330.0,
      "text": "and all her natural systems for a thousand generations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 734330.0,
      "end_time": 736330.0,
      "text": "or 10,000 generations --"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 736330.0,
      "end_time": 739330.0,
      "text": "that is to say, into the indefinite future."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 739330.0,
      "end_time": 744330.0,
      "text": "But does the earth have to wait for our extinction as a species?"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 744330.0,
      "end_time": 747330.0,
      "text": "Well maybe so. But I don&#39;t think so."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 747330.0,
      "end_time": 750330.0,
      "text": "At Interface we really intend to bring this prototypical"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 750330.0,
      "end_time": 753330.0,
      "text": "sustainable, zero-footprint industrial company"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 753330.0,
      "end_time": 756330.0,
      "text": "fully into existence by 2020."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 756330.0,
      "end_time": 758330.0,
      "text": "We can see our way now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 758330.0,
      "end_time": 760330.0,
      "text": "clear to the top of that mountain."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 760330.0,
      "end_time": 763330.0,
      "text": "And now the challenge is in execution."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 763330.0,
      "end_time": 766330.0,
      "text": "And as my good friend and adviser Amory Lovins says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 766330.0,
      "end_time": 770330.0,
      "text": "\"If something exists, it must be possible.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 770330.0,
      "end_time": 773330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 773330.0,
      "end_time": 776330.0,
      "text": "If we can actually do it, it must be possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 776330.0,
      "end_time": 780330.0,
      "text": "If we, a petro-intensive company can do it, anybody can."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 780330.0,
      "end_time": 784330.0,
      "text": "And if anybody can, it follows that everybody can."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 784330.0,
      "end_time": 787330.0,
      "text": "Hawken fulfilled business and industry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 787330.0,
      "end_time": 791330.0,
      "text": "leading humankind away from the abyss"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 791330.0,
      "end_time": 796330.0,
      "text": "because, with continued unchecked decline of the biosphere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 796330.0,
      "end_time": 799330.0,
      "text": "a very dear person is at risk here --"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 799330.0,
      "end_time": 801330.0,
      "text": "frankly, an unacceptable risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 801330.0,
      "end_time": 803330.0,
      "text": "Who is that person?"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 803330.0,
      "end_time": 805330.0,
      "text": "Not you. Not I."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 805330.0,
      "end_time": 808330.0,
      "text": "But let me introduce you to the one who is most at risk here."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 808330.0,
      "end_time": 812330.0,
      "text": "And I myself met this person in the early days of this mountain climb."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 812330.0,
      "end_time": 816330.0,
      "text": "On a Tuesday morning in March of 1996,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 816330.0,
      "end_time": 819330.0,
      "text": "I was talking to people, as I did at every opportunity back then,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 819330.0,
      "end_time": 823330.0,
      "text": "bringing them along and often not knowing whether I was connecting."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 823330.0,
      "end_time": 826330.0,
      "text": "But about five days later back in Atlanta,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 826330.0,
      "end_time": 829330.0,
      "text": "I received an email from Glenn Thomas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 829330.0,
      "end_time": 831330.0,
      "text": "one of my people in the California meeting."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 831330.0,
      "end_time": 833330.0,
      "text": "He was sending me an original poem"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 833330.0,
      "end_time": 836330.0,
      "text": "that he had composed after our Tuesday morning together."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 836330.0,
      "end_time": 840330.0,
      "text": "And when I read it it was one of the most uplifting moments of my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 840330.0,
      "end_time": 844330.0,
      "text": "Because it told me, by God, one person got it."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 844330.0,
      "end_time": 848330.0,
      "text": "Here is what Glenn wrote. And here is that person, most at risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 848330.0,
      "end_time": 852330.0,
      "text": "Please meet \"Tomorrow&#39;s Child.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 852330.0,
      "end_time": 856330.0,
      "text": "\"Without a name, an unseen face, and knowing not your time or place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 856330.0,
      "end_time": 859330.0,
      "text": "Tomorrow&#39;s child, though yet unborn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 859330.0,
      "end_time": 862330.0,
      "text": "I met you first last Tuesday morn."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 862330.0,
      "end_time": 864330.0,
      "text": "A wise friend introduced us two."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 864330.0,
      "end_time": 866330.0,
      "text": "And through his sobering point of view"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 866330.0,
      "end_time": 871330.0,
      "text": "I saw a day that you would see, a day for you but not for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 871330.0,
      "end_time": 873330.0,
      "text": "Knowing you has changed my thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 873330.0,
      "end_time": 875330.0,
      "text": "For I never had an inkling"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 875330.0,
      "end_time": 878330.0,
      "text": "that perhaps the things I do might someday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 878330.0,
      "end_time": 881330.0,
      "text": "somehow threaten you."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 881330.0,
      "end_time": 883330.0,
      "text": "Tomorrow&#39;s child, my daughter, son,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 883330.0,
      "end_time": 885330.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m afraid I&#39;ve just begun to think of you and of your good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 885330.0,
      "end_time": 889330.0,
      "text": "though always having known I should."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 889330.0,
      "end_time": 891330.0,
      "text": "Begin, I will."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 891330.0,
      "end_time": 894330.0,
      "text": "The way the cost of what I squander, what is lost,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 894330.0,
      "end_time": 896330.0,
      "text": "if ever I forget that you"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 896330.0,
      "end_time": 900330.0,
      "text": "will someday come and live here too.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 900330.0,
      "end_time": 902330.0,
      "text": "Well, every day of my life since,"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 902330.0,
      "end_time": 904330.0,
      "text": "\"Tomorrow&#39;s Child\" has spoken to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 904330.0,
      "end_time": 906330.0,
      "text": "with one simple but profound message,"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 906330.0,
      "end_time": 908330.0,
      "text": "which I presume to share with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 908330.0,
      "end_time": 910330.0,
      "text": "We are, each and every one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 910330.0,
      "end_time": 913330.0,
      "text": "a part of the web of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 913330.0,
      "end_time": 917330.0,
      "text": "The continuum of humanity, sure, but in a larger sense, the web of life itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 917330.0,
      "end_time": 919330.0,
      "text": "And we have a choice to make"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 919330.0,
      "end_time": 921330.0,
      "text": "during our brief, brief visit"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 921330.0,
      "end_time": 925330.0,
      "text": "to this beautiful blue and green living planet:"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 925330.0,
      "end_time": 928330.0,
      "text": "to hurt it or to help it."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 928330.0,
      "end_time": 931330.0,
      "text": "For you, it&#39;s your call."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 931330.0,
      "end_time": 933330.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 933330.0,
      "end_time": 948330.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}